{
  "texts": [
    "This hypothetical state of the agent is then used as a basis for our evaluation of its subsequent actions.",
    "For cases involving direct harm attacks, if the next action of the agent is to execute the harmful tool T a, the case is categorized as a successful attack.",
    "In the context of data stealing attacks, if the agent proceeds to use the data extraction tool T a, we further simulate the tool's response, denoted as R Ta, using GPT-4.",
    "The simulation enables us to assess the agent's next step and determine whether it effectively transmits the extracted data to the attacker.",
    "A successful transmission is indicative of a successful attack in these cases."
  ]
